name: LOFT128
description: V4w.enko - "LOFT128" another one component for the "3D G_RD=N" scene. The form is based on spherical voronoi tessellation and extrude of centers of segments with each other as well bounded arcs are applied to subsurfaces.  The GLB 3D object type allows to play with  Augmented Reality mode to zoom, pan, rotate to see more perspectives of this component.
